description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              •	Working with QA Leader to develop process relate to quality.

              •	Working with project manager (PM) to determine project development process base on Company process;

              •	Supporting project to follow process which be defined;

              •	Auditing project weekly to ensuring project’s process;

              •	Reminding deadline for Project manager & team;

              •	Raising project risk/issues; Following issues.

              •	Supporting project to manage customer complaint (investigate, define corrective/prevention action and follow up)

              •	Recording and analyzing project database to identify areas for improvement in the quality

              •	Meeting, reporting, other support if need;


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc

requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              •	At least 2 year experience as PQA in software project; Working with foreign customer.

              •	Bachelors of Science, Computer Science, Mathematics, Engineering degree or equivalent experience;

              •	Have knowledge about implementation methodology such as ISO 27OO1, Scrum, Kaizen;

              •	Have Internal Auditor, Lead Auditor, Scrum master certificate is a plus;

              •	Fluent in English, in both verbal and writing;

              •	Can use Japanese is an advantage;

              *** Personality Requirements:

              •	Hard working, responsible, strong interpersonal and communication skills;

              •	Ability of working independent and teamwork, can work under high pressure;

              •	Have will and interest to learn;

              •	Have service mindset

              •	Open mind

              •	Can support other team member well;


              Interest

              •	Salary: Negotiable. Salary review twice a year

              •	Guided intensive development of technology.

              •	Have the opportunity to work with challenges and develop one’s best abilities.

              •	Health insurance, the social insurance as prescribed by the State.

              •	WORKING ENVIRONMENT: Friendly, dynamic, promotion opportunities.

              •	Receive company’s welfares: Holidays, annual vacation, sports, team building, advanced classes of foreign languages (English, Japanese) ...etc

              •	Health check once a year


              Xem toàn bộ Yêu Cầu Công Việc
